description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Tired of the jazz piano formula of comping with the left hand and soloing with the right, but not sure what else to do? In this lesson, Geoffrey offers an effective step-by-step approach to free up the traditional roles of your hands and help expand your playing "out of the box".  (Level: Intermediate)
title: Geoffrey Keezer - Comping Independence Exercise (Preview)
